com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.DocumentList
public class SPDocumentList
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.enterprise.connector.spi.DocumentList

An implementation of DocumentList Class to represents a list of SPDocuments that are to be sent to GSA. This class holds all the things that should be taken care of 1. when a document is actually sent to CM 2. when checkpoint is received
